@lateralusgamer

Sound like your anti-virus program is disabling the paul.dll file. You need to disable it, add the paul.dll file to the folder, then make an exception path to the game folder so id doesn't keep deleting the file. After the file is in place, you shouldn't get those activation code messages anymore.

Hope that helps.

